videos.headline: Jacobs runs for 9-yard Alabama touchdown
videos.description: Alabama RB Josh Jacobs takes the ball into the end zone as the Crimson Tide get the scoring started early.

videos.headline: Tua throws 13-yard TD pass
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa throws a 13-yard touchdown pass to Henry Ruggs III to increase Alabama's lead to 14-0 early in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Bama's Waddle returns punt for 63-yard touchdown
videos.description: Alabama's Jaylen Waddle returns a punt practically untouched to increase the Tide's lead to 21-0.

videos.headline: Jacobs scores second TD of day
videos.description: RB Josh Jacobs runs the ball in for a 1-yard Alabama touchdown, putting the Tide up 28-0 in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Hurts throws 54-yard TD pass to Ruggs
videos.description: Jalen Hurts enters the game for Alabama, erasing his redshirt chances, and throws a 54-yard touchdown to Henry Ruggs III.

videos.headline: Harris gets into the end zone for Tide TD
videos.description: Alabama RB Najee Harris practically walks into the end zone for a 5-yard Tide touchdown, putting them up 42-0 in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Waddle hits the jets for 94-yard Alabama TD
videos.description: Alabama's Mac Jones throws a short pass to Jaylen Waddle, who takes it all the way for a Crimson Tide touchdown.
